51ef7e17082e26e854478d6f1cefa247","tid":395873,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T08:17:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我記得個時好似有呢單嘢<br />\n高登成班人係咁起底<br />\n最後唔記得左點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔係有記者起左咩?<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20130911/photo/0911-00176-035b2.jpg?t=1505117783027\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20130911%2Fphoto%2F0911-00176-035b2.jpg%3Ft%3D1505117783027&h=2aab490c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple/20130911/large/11la3p2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20130911%2Flarge%2F11la3p2.jpg&h=378bf0a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple/20130911/large/11la3p3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20130911%2Flarge%2F11la3p3.jpg&h=fb21f038&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20130911/photo/0911-00176-035b1.jpg?t=1505117796210\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20130911%2Fphoto%2F0911-00176-035b1.jpg%3Ft%3D1505117796210&h=7b982c7f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fedab74fef336c127bf1d64d525801b9a0713bf3","tid":395873,"uid":1082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T08:17:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>乜撚嘢僕人制服<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  真是淫褻！</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n僕人姐係馬姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.